objects.description: [Stuxnet](https://collaborate.mitre.org/attackics/index.php/Software/S0010) executes malicious SQL commands in the WinCC database server to propagate to remote systems. The malicious SQL commands include xp_cmdshell, sp_dumpdbilog, and sp_addextendedproc.(Citation: Wired W32.Stuxnet Feb 2011)

external_references.description: Nicolas Falliere, Liam O Murchu, Eric Chien. (2011, February). W32.Stuxnet Dossier (Version 1.4). Retrieved September 22, 2017.
